Color in alcohol: carapace yellow with black borders, two brown stripes on thoracic region, abdomen dorsum yellow, with three longitudinal dark stripes, sides with one longitudinal dark stripe (five stripes in total), venter yellow, spinnerets yellow. Femur I yellow, patella, tibia and metatarsus dark; other legs yellow (
